article:
This is a 'list of the manned space missions' conducted by the Russian Federal
Space Agency since 1992. All Russian manned space missions thus far have been
carried out using the Soyuz vehicle.

The Russian Federal Space Agency was the successor to the Soviet space program.
Numeration of the Soyuz flights therefore continues from previous Soviet Soyuz
launches. For previous flights of the Soyuz and other manned space vehicles, see
List of Soviet manned space missions.
